{"tid":541111,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Monster Hunter World (7) SOS求救","createTime":"2018-01-26T06:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T07:11:59.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"74271917c9dc9b63fdd0c92fa5370e0e2d5eb50f","tid":541111,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.monsterhunterworld.com/images/share.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunterworld.com%2Fimages%2Fshare.png&h=c727d2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n資訊頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6b3255dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<br />\n新手Q&amp;A<br />\nQ : 玩咩武器好?<br />\nA : 覺得邊樣型就玩邊樣<br />\n<br />\nQ : 多唔多人用 弓/笛/鎚/乜乜物物<br />\nA : 多<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ : 幾時有中文更新?<br />\nA : 26號以Patch形式下載<br />\n<br />\nQ : 玩男角定女角?<br />\nA : 隨你<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ :有無人開個新手群？<br />\nA : 冇，有咩就係度講/係度約戰<br />\n<br />\nQ :點解連唔到線既?<br />\nA: 因為要俾錢買PS plus<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有冇pc版？幾時出？<br />\nA: 預計2018秋季出，除此之外咩情報都冇<br />\n<br />\nQ : 買左日英文版...係咪要買返中文版?<br />\nA : 睇說明啦文盲<br />\n<br />\nQ: 噴血少左點算好<br />\nA: 設定係咁<br />\n<br />\nQ: 傷害數字好撚核突可唔可以整走<br />\nA: Option有得較走<br />\n<br />\nQ: LOCK人有冇得用番3DS果款<br />\nA: Option有得set<br />\n<br />\nQ:買錯日英版點算?<br />\nA:屌你老母個老母"},{"pid":"8a2a81634a7e950a7b68d4fdde5ebb82a30250e4","tid":541111,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77434fc78bfae714ca429be263c07a75b7199963","tid":541111,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislik