:"3cb7bb1047dcc549b3cd55cc4803c5ab22f0dbca","tid":541111,"uid":164708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ce6d3c53abae8fa4c6dfffbf03d61ca66b7f17a","tid":541111,"uid":34243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1001開post係慣例 唔好做壞規矩</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:11:11.000Z","msg":"咁撚狗巴打記住更新Q&amp;A<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314c1f22744f27f6564b0a3d35cf3e9cbe13a6c3","tid":541111,"uid":137764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"開過啦, 更新埋Q&amp;A"},{"pid":"8da997eea4f6d08e660d70d463e6a04d4f415335","tid":541111,"uid":34243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:11:13.000Z","msg":"[quote]<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.monsterhunterworld.com/images/share.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunterworld.com%2Fimages%2Fshare.png&h=c727d2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n資訊頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6b3255dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手Q&amp;A<br />\nQ : 玩咩武器好?<br />\nA : 覺得邊樣型就玩邊樣<br />\n<br />\nQ : 一開始用咩裝好?<br />\nA : 下位睇防禦力就可以 一係就飛雷龍<br />\n<br />\nQ : 多唔多人用 弓/笛/鎚/乜乜物物<br />\nA : 多<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ : 玩男角定女角?<br />\nA : 隨你<br />\n<br />\nQ : 咩武器高輸出<br />\nA : 用得勁, 咩武器都高輸出<br />\n<br />\nQ :有無人開個新手群？<br />\nA : 冇，有咩就係度講/係度約戰<br />\n<br />\nQ :點解連唔到線既?<br />\nA: 因為要俾錢買PS plus<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有冇pc版？幾時出？<br />\nA: 預計2018秋季出，除此之外咩情報都冇<br />\n<br />\nQ : 買左日英文版...係咪要買返中文版?<br />\nA : 睇說明啦文盲<br />\n<br />\nQ: 噴血少左點算好<br />\nA: 設定係咁<br />\n<br />\nQ: 傷害數字好撚核突可唔可以整走<br />\nA: Option有得較走<br />\n<br />\nQ: LOCK人有冇得用番3DS果款<br />\nA: Option有得set<br />\n<br />\nQ:買錯日英版點算?<br />\nA:屌你老母個老母<br />\n<br />\nQ.大家同一進度點樣可以一齊clear/故事進度不足<br />\nA.低進度入唔到高進度個任,你要先觸發劇情 去到見到條龍 可以發出SOS訊號既位<br />\n之後quit任 再重開就可以一齊玩一齊clear<br />\n<br />\nQ. 順風護石係邊到拎<br />\nA. redeem完係房個貓<br />\n<br />\nQ.開左角色之後,可唔可以重設?改唔改到名?<br />\nA.骨架類嘅整唔到,名改唔到<br />\n<br />\nQ.Horizon 個任一開就解散<br />\nA.個任有bug"},{"pid":"4308b1a3794cc5b392357d921706a51907408ef6","tid":541111,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:12:04.000Z","msg":"大家幾防"},{"pid":"4321b1c5102d1ec5c62a0e21a17523de032e2127","tid":541111,"uid":32830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:13:33.000Z","msg":"屌唔識開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇整到張圖"},{"pid":"4a2caaf3d24c9637a04714f411bd61563f849430","tid":541111,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:13:36.000Z","msg":"諗起<br />\n有無人有行耐未滿既幻覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一望血耐就想食肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b2dd1ea8a25a9dce47261fefaca5a77aed6600","tid":541111,"uid":118865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"女裝黎講 暫時 蠻顎龍個裝唔差"},{"pid":"94ed7a80ba80543373e5388c0617e556920dc962","tid":541111,"uid":82651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"今集連線真係有點柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c56db2d22b343da828716f830410b9bcb00745","tid":541111,"uid":154505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:28:22.000Z","msg":"個post死左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337839e60e319f0647c42bf3e4bad72ad9e7295d","tid":541111,"uid":43209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:30:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起<br 